Now that people are starting to watch it, I feel bound to say that this video is inspired by Hannibal || Glitter & Gold - Voordeel, the background music is Glitter & Gold by Barns Courtney.

summary: s1: marching for danny / s3: marching in solidarity against sexual violence broadchurch at its heart is about communities coming...
caption:
s1: marching for danny / s3: marching in solidarity against sexual violence

broadchurch at its heart is about communities coming together to overcome trauma, and to reaffirm that they will not allow themselves to be broken by brutality. no surprise, then, that they chose to bring back this imagery twice: specks of light held aloft, swaths of brightness cutting through the dark.
